The paper focuses on the citedness and altmetrics of research data, which falls under the domain of digital libraries (cs.DL) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The study also explores the relationship between research data and social media, which could be relevant to cybersecurity (cs.CR) and social computing (cs.SI).
